column1: UNC_Marchetti_diatom_cultures_IP-DAG_pmol_totals.csv, mass data for certain IP-DAG identified in West Antarctic diatom isolates provided by A. Marchetti and C. Moreno, University of North Carolina
Identifications were made by J. Collins, james.r.collins@aya.yale.edu, using v1.1.1 of the LOBSTAHS lipidomics software package for R
Quantification was performed using authentic standards as described in J. Collins' Ph.D. thesis

Values in columns 14-22 of this file are in units of total picomoles per extract (from modified Bligh and Dyer extract of entire culture sample on GF/F filter, with scaling based on observed quantity of internal standard)
